      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 五组都确认：panel / taxonomy / eligibility / shared_feature_base / delivery\n2. 真实在 research repo 落盘，不是空目录或占位文件\n3. panel_manifest、membership、mask、coverage、shared_feature_base 都要生成\n4. machine-readable 产物都补 artifact_catalog 与 field_dictionary\n5. 通过 review closure 后，才能进入 04 CSF Signal Ready",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 五组都确认：panel / taxonomy / eligibility / shared_feature_base / delivery\n2. 真实在 research repo 落盘，不是空目录或占位文件\n3. panel_manifest、membership、mask、coverage、shared_feature_base 都要生成\n4. machine-readable 产物都补 artifact_catalog 与 field_dictionary\n5. 通过 review closure 后，才能进入 04 CSF Signal Ready",
