      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "真正冻结的是研究底座坐标系：\n- panel_primary_key = date × asset\n- cross_section_time_key\n- asset_key\n- universe membership\n- eligibility base mask\n- coverage 语义\n- shared feature base\n\n它回答的是：同一时点哪些资产可比。",
