    {
      "id": "example-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1420,
      "width": 795,
      "height": 214,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#115e59",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ab6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1057,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2057,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "假设你的研究题目是：BTC 出现 1m downside shock 之后，哪些 ALT 在接下来更脆弱。Data Ready 这一步不会直接告诉你“做空 SOL”或“做多 XRP”。\n\n它先把同一时点的横截面底座准备出来。比如在 `2025-01-02 10:05` 这个时点，先形成这样的 base rows：\n- `date=10:05, asset=SOLUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=1, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=L1`\n- `date=10:05, asset=DOGEUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=0, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=Meme`\n- `date=10:05, asset=XRPUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=1, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=Payments`\n\n这一步准备的是：谁在正式 universe 里、谁当前可研究、共享字段值是什么、哪些行因为 coverage 或 liquidity 问题不能参与排序。\n后面的 Signal Ready 才会在这套底座上计算 factor score。",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "假设你的研究题目是：BTC 出现 1m downside shock 之后，哪些 ALT 在接下来更脆弱。Data Ready 这一步不会直接告诉你“做空 SOL”或“做多 XRP”。\n\n它先把同一时点的横截面底座准备出来。比如在 `2025-01-02 10:05` 这个时点，先形成这样的 base rows：\n- `date=10:05, asset=SOLUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=1, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=L1`\n- `date=10:05, asset=DOGEUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=0, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=Meme`\n- `date=10:05, asset=XRPUSDT, in_universe=1, eligible=1, ret_1m=..., quote_volume_3d_med=..., beta_input=..., sector=Payments`\n\n这一步准备的是：谁在正式 universe 里、谁当前可研究、共享字段值是什么、哪些行因为 coverage 或 liquidity 问题不能参与排序。\n后面的 Signal Ready 才会在这套底座上计算 factor score。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "hasTextLink": false
    },
